  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4832126">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4832126/" class="title-link">阴符经（探讨帖）</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4832126"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lovingness/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u35433045-58.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lovingness/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">时间、时间</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-03-13"
      class="main-meta">2011-03-13 21:02:53</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4832126_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                          阴符经不过区区三四百字么，神在哪里诡秘在哪里呢，为何会被视为经典？  对此我是弄不明白的，主要原因我想是才疏学浅，对中国古人的思想了解太少。缺乏整体的关照，自然无法给这篇经文一个合适的定位。 于是我对这篇经文的解读也就只是以我现有的全部知识、经验、直觉...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4832126/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4832126_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4832126_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
