  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6463551">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6463551/" class="title-link">社会的运行的奥秘——【时机】——*咿呀呦*</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6463551"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/love_reading/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u56296947-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/love_reading/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">知道一丶</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-12-16"
      class="main-meta">2013-12-16 14:47:58</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6463551_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是一本神奇的书，振聋发聩。语言，用词都有很高的艺术性，其内容更是深刻。如此深刻的内容用朴素的语言表达出来，不敢想象先人的智慧究竟到了什么程度。 这本书，文字简短。全篇要告诉我们最重要的道理就是做任何事，看任何事都要看准时机。掌握时机是一种极其难能可贵的才能...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6463551_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6463551_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










